        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Top Question of the Week"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "li",
          "value": "Is it really necessary to authentically be web3?"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "Yes. Full stop."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Most Common Repeat Question"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "li",
          "value": "How do you authentically be web3?"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "This question is multi-layered and nuanced, but, at the same time, it’s very straight forward. To be authentically web3 it means decentralisation across capital, technology, culture, governance and content. But also it means taking a long hard look at yourself in the mirror and thinking about what motivates you, what principles you align with, and, what you are really dedicated to make happen."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Top Controversies in the Industry"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "I mean, in short, yes, yes it is. It’s a protection racket for incumbents and it’s framed as if it is to protect the common person. DeFi is meant to change this, but frankly, it’s not fully doing it yet, rather, so much of it is just exit liquidity for the same few."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*HldsTfzr-LMJw1wYiDtFNg.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Silly Fails and Trolling"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "Is there really anything to say? 😆"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*-MhjWoExeNA9PWoFfhAoyQ.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "View all FUD FAQ here."
        },
